e":"2019-07-28T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"KEEP住仲有！！！"},{"pid":"d4215fb6b7a47d126bcc7ed7c4e2339ec1bf87ed","tid":1377754,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"玩包抄"},{"pid":"0805342be2151482a77725bdf8dc4c6b7436994d","tid":1377754,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"幫手推畀現場人睇"},{"pid":"35c2f682ad386122f2041481231395a7af65bf26","tid":1377754,"uid":249242,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"我唔會話散，但今晚有機會全軍覆沒。"},{"pid":"964d9d198c5022320789c6aaa91be86b7be4a36a","tid":1377754,"uid":70830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d765333c5b524777e9d591b9cf0b2c7df14c24d","tid":1377754,"uid":70830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"9313dd5da2317b9a41641ba842687b51fc12fa1d","tid":1377754,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"快啲推畀現場人知"},{"pid":"dfe87dfb12ba9384a8af32030d372ae87bad87d8","tid":1377754,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:39:41.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再開post或屌或問或指輝，要都等撒哂人先<br />\n<br />\n而且前線有前線決定，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每個決定都係剎那間做決定</span></span>，我地插唔到咀<br />\n<br />\n我地可以幫嘅係幫手推返啲有用有資訊嘅上去<br />\n巴絲係前線無咁多時間check嘢搵嘢，推上去可以令佢地係熱門一搵就搵到，你地都見速龍幾快，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多啲資料佢地先唔會做錯決定</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有地圖po請推，電視係一睇就睇到好多好多，但<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線睇唔到電視完全無機會收到最新消息</span></span>，完全唔知狗點安排<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">（希望有巴絲可以以直播嘅資訊整地圖，好似元朗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另跪求文宣整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>612基金介紹嘅醫療團體</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/368482457185258/posts/389730678393769?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F368482457185258%2Fposts%2F389730678393769%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=fee49674\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/368482457185258/posts/389730678393769?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重申多一次，唔明點解前線要留既請入，前線只會係以下三種情況下徹退。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者唔怕身體受傷，但怕坐監有案底，不過我地可以令義士連有案底都冇咁驚</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1323509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1323509</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我係急症室醫生，教你發夢受傷點樣睇醫生。</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1376835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1376835</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">醫生：發夢被捕時不要上警車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377451</a></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">【瘋狂置頂】請 立 即 不 斷 課 金 支 援 所 有 受 傷 被 捕 義 士！！！！！(2)</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319141</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[初心]希望大家仲記得呢八個字 兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374070</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"c286ab8596a4ac8d8b0254b9bd1305efc35543a1","tid":1377754,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"等現場有準備，如果唔係好快玩完"},{"pid":"4b7529ffbdcf14dc2f1c981d862ceb24baecd777","tid":1377754,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d765333c5b524777e9d591b9cf0b2c7df14c24d","tid":1377754,"uid":70830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打"},{"pid":"b2c576ac1b6fa4e4ffca3516082a160fc289a62e","tid":1377754,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5663f04efdd075f1a4bc4740653efddfc024c6c1","tid":1377754,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96325a76a7e790578b2de8b509dcf3f6a0321f8a","tid":1377754,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"82d4e26a6d2642679e71c1b76c92a1409522d80a","tid":1377754,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"報比哨兵"},{"pid":"12a8c55a8b5697d42abd3600b223c9144292798e","tid":1377754,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d4e26a6d2642679e71c1b76c92a1409522d80a","tid":1377754,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"報比哨兵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"報咗未佢未睇"},{"pid":"8d4a991d2595cd67a85c87655437e1ffcd7a7c4f","tid":1377754,"uid":289